Game.....: Surf Rocket Racer
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: March 1st, 2001
Ripped.......: Nothing

Eurasia's release from about a month ago was PAL/50HZ only, and noone ever made a 60HZ/NTSC patch for it. Here is the USA version of the game which is playable for users in America and Asia. Hop in the saddle of your jetbike and get ready to hit the waveswith Crave's Surf Rocket Racer! Dreamcast's superior graphicabilities are put to good use with 7 full levels of eye-catchingbackdrops and realistic sparkling water, and you'll want to takeadvantage of the splitscreen VS mode to challenge all those whooppose you!